                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div> Share
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


</div>


    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>09 May 1940</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 360</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-1f76fc95-d7d6-4114-adb1-fec275c825f3'>
            
<p class="">45.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c">
                Mr. Hely-Hutchinson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-09/debates/77d2216e-947a-47c8-9cbc-2b1a5f8da412/ArmedForces(Co-Ordination)#contribution-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether there is any staff course for senior officers of all three Services to provide an opportunity for the study of operations, involving the co-ordination of all three arms under a single command, with a view to making officers who have passed such a course eligible for appointment to such a command?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-09/debates/77d2216e-947a-47c8-9cbc-2b1a5f8da412/ArmedForces(Co-Ordination)#contribution-05469e39-1e57-4039-a98a-053da4d75d2c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Chamberlain)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-09/debates/77d2216e-947a-47c8-9cbc-2b1a5f8da412/ArmedForces(Co-Ordination)#contribution-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Up to the outbreak of war, the study of operations involving the co-ordination of all three arms (whether under joint command, unified command or command by the Service playing the predominant part) had been for many years the subject of particular study not only at the Imperial Defence College, but also at the staff colleges of the three Services. The courses at these colleges were closed on <span id="1397" class="column-number" data-column-number="1397"></span> the outbreak of war, but it is clear that there are a number of senior officers who are qualified by their training for the command of combined operations.<p></p> In addition, an establishment known as the Inter-Service Training and Development Centre was set up by His Majesty's Government in September, 1938, with the following terms of reference: <blockquote><q>"To study and develop the material, technique and tactics necessary for all types of combined operations."</q></blockquote> This Centre is still in being, and functioning at full pressure.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-09/debates/77d2216e-947a-47c8-9cbc-2b1a5f8da412/ArmedForces(Co-Ordination)#contribution-acb7b6c0-c4e8-4867-bf39-be1b1ceb88c1">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





